; ---- 3-layer square perimeter demo ----
; Typical FDM settings: nozzle 205C, bed 60C, PLA
M140 S60        ; bed temp target
M104 S205       ; nozzle temp target

; Home and lift
G1 Z5.0 F600
G1 X110 Y110 F9000   ; move to center (travel)

; ----- Layer 1 : Z=0.20 -----
G1 Z0.20 F600
G1 X20 Y20 F9000     ; travel to start corner

; Outer perimeter
